          <div class="editorial-meta">
            <span class="editorial-date">2026-06-15</span>
            <span class="editorial-read" tabindex="0">阅读全文</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="editorial-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="editorial-img">
          <div class="editorial-img-inner">🇦🇺</div>
          <span class="editorial-tag">澳洲留学</span>
        </div>
        <div class="editorial-body">
          <h3 class="editorial-title">澳大利亚留学一年生活费换汇策略：分几批换最合理？</h3>
          <p class="editorial-excerpt">实测对比分3批、6批换汇与一次性换汇的成本差异，附RBA利率周期与澳元走势参考。</p>
          <div class="editorial-meta">
            <span class="editorial-date">2026-06-08</span>
            <span class="editorial-read" tabindex="0">阅读全文</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="editorial-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="editorial-img">
          <div class="editorial-img-inner">🏦</div>
          <span class="editorial-tag">银行实操</span>
        </div>
        <div class="editorial-body">
          <h3 class="editorial-title">工商银行、建行国际汇款留学优惠汇率申请全流程</h3>
          <p class="editorial-excerpt">凭录取通知书可申请的留学专项汇款汇率优惠，附材料清单和申请注意事项。</p>
          <div class="editorial-meta">
            <span class="editorial-date">2026-05-29</span>
            <span class="editorial-read" tabindex="0">阅读全文</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
